       <em>
        n
       </em>
       ), enthalpy (ΔH) and association constant (
       <em>
        K
       </em>
       <sub>
        b
       </sub>
       ) using the least squares minimization routines provided in the Origin software. The values of these parameters obtained for each interaction are shown. (
